  "description": "Use this skill to configure Field Service Lightning service resources \u2014 including ServiceResource types, skill assignments via ServiceResourceSkill, capacity-based resource setup, and ResourcePreference rules. NOT for service territory setup (see fsl-service-territory-setup), NOT for scheduling policy configuration, and NOT for FSL mobile app setup.",
